"false\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors duration-150\">USD<svg width=\"8\" height=\"5\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 5\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200\"><path d=\"M1 1l3 3 3-3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/thekvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"KVRN on Instagram\" class=\"text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" rx=\"5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></rect><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></circle><circle cx=\"17.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\"1\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></a><a href=\"https://tiktok.com/@thekvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"KVRN on TikTok\" class=\"text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 27\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19.5 3.2A5.6 5.6 0 0114 0h-3.7v18.3a2.9 2.9 0 11-2.8-3 2.9 2.9 0 011 .2V11.6a7 7 0 10.6 13.7V13.8a9.1 9.1 0 005.4 1.7V12a5.6 5.6 0 01-3.3-1.1A5.5 5.5 0 0014 12V3.7a9.3 9.3 0 005.5 1.6V1.8l-.05 1.4z\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[300] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-label=\"Shopping bag\" class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 bottom-0 z-[400] w-full max-w-[400px] bg-kvrn-bg flex flex-col transition-transform duration-[500ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 border-b border-kvrn-border\"><h2 class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase\">Bag </h2><button aria-label=\"Close bag\" class=\"p-2 -mr-2 text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3l12 12M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full px-6 text-center gap-5\"><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">Your bag is empty.</p><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-transparent text-kvrn-text border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-kvrn-text hover:text-kvrn-bg active:bg-[#333333] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-10 px-5 text-[11px]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a href=\"/shop\">Browse products</a></span></button></div></div></div><main id=\"main-content\"><div class=\"pt-[calc(36px+56px)]\"><div class=\"container-kvrn section-padding max-w-3xl\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-10\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted tracking-wide\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\" href=\"/support/faq\">Support</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li class=\"text-kvrn-text\" aria-current=\"page\">Shipping &amp; Returns</li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"font-display font-light text-[40px] md:text-[52px] leading-none tracking-tighter mb-16\">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1><section class=\"mb-16\" aria-labelledby=\"shipping-h\"><h2 id=\"shipping-h\" class=\"label-11 mb-6\">Shipping</h2><div class=\"space-y-5 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>Orders are processed within approximately<!-- --> <strong class=\"font-light text-kvrn-text\">1–3 business days</strong> <!-- -->of payment confirmation. Products are not available for preorder unless explicitly stated.</p><p>Shipping costs vary based on destination, selected method, and package size. Exact costs are calculated at checkout.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6\"><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-4\"><p class=\"label-11 mb-1\">Domestic delivery</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">2–7 business days</p></div><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-4\"><p class=\"label-11 mb-1\">International delivery</p><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light\">5–14+ business days</p></div></div><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Delivery estimates are not guarantees. Factors outside our control — including customs processing, carrier delays, and weather — may affect timelines.</p><p>Every order includes tracking. You will receive a shipping confirmation with a tracking link when your order dispatches.</p><p>Complimentary shipping is available on qualifying orders — see the checkout page or our shipping progress bar for current thresholds.</p></div></section><div class=\"rule mb-16\"></div><section id=\"returns\" class=\"mb-16\" aria-labelledby=\"returns-h\"><h2 id=\"returns-h\" class=\"label-11 mb-6\">Returns</h2><div class=\"space-y-5 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>We accept returns for<!-- --> <strong class=\"font-light text-kvrn-text\">store credit</strong> <!-- -->on eligible items within our return window.</p><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border bg-kvrn-bg-raised p-5 text-[13px] space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-kvrn-text font-light mb-2\">Why store credit?</p><p>Store credit allows us to continue investing in product quality rather than increasing prices. We believe it&#x27;s a fair exchange — and you keep full value to spend on any future product.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex gap-5 pb-5 border-b border-kvrn-border last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><span class=\"label-11 text-kvrn-muted flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 min-w-[24px]\">01</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-1\">Check eligibility</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Items must be unworn, unwashed, in original condition, with tags still attached. Items showing signs of use or washing cannot be accepted.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 pb-5 border-b border-kvrn-border last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><span class=\"label-11 text-kvrn-muted flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 min-w-[24px]\">02</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-1\">Initiate your return</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Email returns@kvrn.shop with your order number and the item(s) you wish to return. We will respond within 24 hours with instructions.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 pb-5 border-b border-kvrn-border last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><span class=\"label-11 text-kvrn-muted flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 min-w-[24px]\">03</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-1\">Ship back to us</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Pack the items securely and ship them using a tracked service. Customer is responsible for return shipping costs, except in cases of faulty, damaged, or incorrect items.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 pb-5 border-b border-kvrn-border last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><span class=\"label-11 text-kvrn-muted flex-shrink-0 pt-0.5 min-w-[24px]\">04</span><div><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-1\">Receive store credit</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Once we receive and inspect your return, we will issue store credit for the item value. Store credit does not expire.</p></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"rule mb-16\"></div><section class=\"mb-16\" aria-labelledby=\"exceptions-h\"><h2 id=\"exceptions-h\" class=\"label-11 mb-6\">Exceptions</h2><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Faulty, damaged, or incorrectly shipped items: full refund or replacement at our cost, including return shipping.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Final sale items, if designated as such, are not eligible for return.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Items that have been worn, washed, or altered cannot be accepted.</li></ul></section><section><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light mb-2\">Questions?</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">Email<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:returns@kvrn.shop\" class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\">returns@kvrn.shop</a> <!-- -->— we respond within 24 hours.</p></section></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-kvrn-border bg-kvrn-bg\" aria-label=\"Site footer\"><div class=\"container-kvrn\"><div class=\"py-12 md:py-14 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-6\"><div class=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-1 space-y-4\"><a class=\"block text-[14px] font-display font-light tracking-wider uppercase\" href=\"/\">KVRN</a><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Quiet luxury.<br/>Premium utility.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/thekvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"KVRN on Instagram (@thekvrn)\" class=\"text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors duration-150\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" rx=\"5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></rect><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></circle><circle cx